text:
Shell Bank Creek (Brooklyn): Viewing from Plumb Island toward Gerritsen Beach in the background. View 2 shows the northern end of the creek and a new sewer between Sheepshead Bay and Plumb Beach.

July 7, 1935
Views 1, 2

P. L. Sperr
title: Bank Shell Creek - Brooklyn - [Plumb Island.]
